Maintainer: Bryan Whiting <seekgospelanalysis@gmail.com>
Description: Ever want to generate a quote you can share on social media or in an Rmarkdown
  file? This package will take in some text you provide (html/markdown accepted)
  and will produce a simple plot with plain background.
